## PROJECT
Unified Trading System V3.0
Dual-track: MT5/FTMO prop firm + IBKR Canada RRSP
Owner: Waterloo, Ontario, Canada
Goal: $500 CAD → $15K–30K/month in 36 months
Documentation: EVERYTHING_FINAL.md (16,552 lines)

## MODEL ROUTING — USE EXACTLY THESE MODELS

### claude-opus-4-6 — USE FOR:
- ANY Dhatu framework logic (15 types, sutra freshness, ABHAVA)
- Bayesian belief tracker implementation (M-02, F8, F17)
- Shannon entropy / signal entropy (M-01)
- CatalystScorer — F3 order of operations (most critical)
- Architecture decisions, cross-agent dependencies
- Reading + reasoning about full documentation
- Brain coordinator, state machine, IPC design
- Anything requiring 200K context (full codebase review)

### claude-sonnet-4-6 — USE FOR:
- Pattern detection (bull flag, H&S, falling wedge, oversold bounce, sector sympathy)
- MultiTimeframeAligner, EscapeVelocityClassifier
- Integration layer (main.py, wiring agents together)
- Writing + running tests
- Code review of other agents' outputs
- Refactoring, documentation, README updates
- Quick questions about the codebase

### gpt-5.4 — USE FOR:
- Kelly criterion + Half-Kelly sizing (M-03)
- Fat-tail risk adjustments (M-07, all instrument multipliers)
- F6 8-step position sizing chain (ALL 8 steps required)
- Instrument volume thresholds (F5, all 8 instruments)
- FTMO compliance rules (4%/8%/2trades/Best Day Rule)
- VIX intraday protocol (F11)
- Correlation cascade defense (F13)
- Black Swan protocol (F14)
- Any precise financial calculation with strict numerical rules
- IBKR ib_insync connection + execution
- MT5 MetaTrader5 API connection + execution

### gemini-3.1-pro-preview — USE FOR:
- Regime classifier (BULL/BEAR/VOLATILE/CHOPPY/TRENDING)
- Statistical significance gate (M-04, n-based ratings)
- Edge crowding detector (M-05, Nash equilibrium)
- System entropy monitor (P-01, thermodynamic decay)
- Conditional expectancy matrix (activates at n≥200)
- Partial exit rules per pattern (F9)
- Resolution window calibration (F10)
- Walk-forward validation
- Weekly/monthly calibration pipeline
- Queries needing real-time market context

